    dc:description "FIGURE 1. General aspect of the stream where tadpoles of Boana stellae were found (A) and exact pond in which the tadpoles were collected (B). General ventral and dorsal view of the preserved tadpole of B. stellae, MCP 13202 stage 30 (C, D), and detail of the oral disc of MCP 13201 stage 25 (E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3713963/files/figure.png" ;
